
'''= CCTA)is an association of professionals and business owners who trade products and services for other things they need.  CCTA members reduce expenses and increase sales by doing business with each other without using cash.'''

URL = http://www.communityconnecttrade.com/

=Description=

'CCTA’s customer service agents help you to bring the new customers that you are looking for and offset cash expenses by exchanging products and services with other CCTA member businesses. Members can also find you through our online directory. The members who buy your products and services pay you with trade credits. Each trade credit is equal to one dollar in value.  You use your trade credits to buy products and services from other member businesses.”


